Swansea have expressed an interest in Montpellier holding midfielder Benjamin Stambouli. 

The 23-year-old also has also been earmarked by Fiorentina.

Garry Monk has already signed France striker Bafetimbi Gomis this summer and could move to bring his countryman to Wales, too.  

