QPR midfielder Adel Taarabt meanwhile, is the subject of a £3million bid from AC Milan.

The Italians will also offer a percentage sell on to the London club.

Taarabt spent six months at the San Siro on loan, but Milan refused to pay the agreed buy-out clause.

